page.title: 06Diary 5
page.content: Jennifer Shovell I get up at about 7.30-8.00 on Saturday mornings.I normally go to call for my freind Karen.There is only pavement for about 1/5 of the way.I see about 2 people on the way.On the way back we would go into the shop to get some shopping,small things only for big things we go to Launceston. Karen and I play games like sevensies. At 10.0clock Karen goes homeand Mum takes me to ballet Mum takes me in the car the roads are windy on the way.At about 12.00clock Mum picks me up.We go home and have fish & chips from Five lanes a place about 7 miles away from Lewannick where I live.1.00clock Karen comes up go, to Grans 5.00clock come home have tea,watch TV 9.00clock bed.
